<% content_for :title, "Data Protection Officer - Kubera" %>

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Data Protection Officer</h1>

  <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-800 space-y-6">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300">
        For all data protection inquiries, including requests to access, correct, or delete your personal data:
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-indigo-400 font-medium">
        DPO: dpo@kubera.app
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Your Rights Under DPDP Act 2023</h2>
      <ul class="text-gray-300 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
        <li><strong>Right to知情 (Knowledge):</strong> You have the right to know what personal data we collect and how it is used.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to Consent:</strong> We will obtain your explicit consent before processing your data for any purpose.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to Access:</strong> You can request a copy of all personal data we hold about you.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to Correction:</strong> You can request correction of inaccurate or incomplete data.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to Deletion:</strong> You can request deletion of your personal data at any time.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to Grievance Redressal:</strong> You can file complaints regarding data processing.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Data We Collect</h2>
      <ul class="text-gray-300 space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Email address and profile information (via Google OAuth)</li>
        <li>Financial data you choose to enter (debts, investments, transactions, budgets)</li>
        <li>Usage data to improve our services</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Data Retention</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300">
        We retain your data only as long as necessary to provide our services. Upon account deletion, all personal data is permanently erased within 48 hours.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
